  <trk>
    <name>Leuk sun mountains</name>
    <desc>Scenic hike through the regional nature park Pfyn-Finges from the mountain village Jeizinen along the sunny south flank of the Rhone Valley to Leuk. Discover the village of Erschmatt with its Rye Centre as well as the satellite ground station above Leuk.</desc>
